#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:2
msgid "检测与反馈"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:4
msgid "本章说明如何在系统中创建并执行检测任务、查看历史记录与反馈数据，以及通过反馈迭代模型的基本流程。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:-1
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:11
msgid "新建检测任务"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:13
msgid "完成 PCB 产品创建并训练后，返回主页，点击 **新建检测任务**。在弹窗中完成任务配置："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:15
msgid "**传送带**：选择对应的传送带（conveyor）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:16
msgid "**选择一个 PCBA**：选择目标 PCB 产品。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:17
msgid "**选择任务模式**：如 **自动连续运行任务**，适用于正式生产；调试阶段可逐板查看。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:18
msgid "**以演示模式运行**：在无实物 / 无硬件条件下回放演示数据，可用于培训或流程验证。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:20
msgid "完成后点击 **开始检测**。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:27
msgid "连续检测错误处理"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:29
msgid "在连续检测模式下，遇到错误时系统是否自动停止由 `pause_when_ng` 配置项控制（参考 :ref:`系统JSON配置`）。说明如下："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:31
msgid ""
"`true`：检测到 "
"NG（不良）或发生异常时，系统会自动暂停当前任务并停留在出错的子板位置，便于现场人工查看、定位并处理该子板；同时该条记录会被标记为不良并写入任务数据。此选项适用于需要逐板确认或即时干预的生产场景。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:32
msgid ""
"`false`：发生 NG "
"时系统不会中断生产，会按既定节拍继续运行并记录该子板为不良（或按设定分拣策略处理）。此模式适用于对产线吞吐要求较高且容许事后抽查或自动分拣的场景。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:35
msgid "检测页面概览"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:37
msgid "进入检测页面后，界面元素与操作："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:-1
msgid "检测页面"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:43
msgid "**空格**：进板并立即开始检测。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:44
msgid "**左侧控制按钮**：进板 | 出板 | 通过 | 复位，用于手动控制生产节拍。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:45
msgid ""
"**右侧信息栏**：实时显示产品统计（合格 / 不合格数量）、元件统计（合格率 / 不良率 / 误报率）与检测时长；良率可在 "
"**整板（Board）** 与 **子板（Sub-board）** 口径之间切换（拼板产品按实际子板数统计）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:-1
msgid "检测复审页面"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:51
msgid "检测到缺陷时，系统会自动跳转到缺陷详情视图，可查看放大图、定位框、缺陷类型和判定依据，并可立即进行人工反馈（判为良品/不良/忽略等）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:55
msgid "双轨检测系统"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:-1
msgid "双轨检测示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:61
msgid "对于配置了双轨检测的系统，检测页面会同时显示左右两条传送带的并行检测视图；操作与单轨系统类似，但在视图切换与记录检索上增加了分轨能力："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:63
msgid "按 `Enter` 会查询未读的检测记录，默认优先显示左轨，随后显示右轨（两轨独立计数与统计）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:64
msgid "通过上方标签页在“左轨 / 右轨”间切换，分别查看各自的历史记录与缺陷详情。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:68
msgid "快捷键"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:71
msgid "检测页面快捷键 (缺陷详情视图)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:77
msgid ""
"`1–0`（数字键）：在缺陷详情视图中快速反馈对应的预设类别；按住 `Ctrl` + 数字键 可访问扩展类别（例如 `Ctrl`+`1` 表示类别"
" 11）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:78
msgid "方向键 `上` / `下`：切换上一条 / 下一条缺陷记录。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:79
msgid "方向键 `左` / `右`：在同一元件的不同缺陷类型之间切换（例如主体与引脚的缺陷视图）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:80
msgid "`Enter`：返回上一个检测记录；若当前为最新记录，则返回检测概览页面。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:81
msgid "`空格`：进板并开始检测。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:84
msgid "编程页面快捷键"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:86
msgid "`Ctrl+C` / `Ctrl+V`：复制并粘贴当前元件（包含所有检测框与属性）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:87
msgid "`W` / `A` / `S` / `D`：在选中检测框时微调框的位置；在选中移动工具时移动视图。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:88
msgid "`V`：切换到选择工具。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:89
msgid "`H`：切换到移动（拖拽）工具。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:90
msgid "`1`：切换到主体工具。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:91
msgid "`2`：切换到焊料工具。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:92
msgid "`3`：切换到 IC 引脚工具。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:93
msgid "`4`：切换到 OCR（文本）工具。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:94
msgid "`5`：切换到条形码工具。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:97
msgid "缺陷详情与快速反馈"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:99
msgid "在缺陷详情页中："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:101
msgid "查看放大图与定位框，确认缺陷区域与具体判别依据。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:102
msgid "使用快捷键或界面按钮进行快速反馈（例如标记为误报、确认不良、忽略等）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:103
msgid "反馈会写入该产品的数据集，供后续训练与参数调整使用。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:122
msgid "所有缺陷类别（界面显示）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:106
msgid "下面列举基于界面右侧缺陷反馈面板的缺陷类别（按显示顺序编号）："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:108
msgid "无错误"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/inspection/index.rst:109
msgid "缺件"
msgstr ""

